{
  "stem": "18186.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 406.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe I was 13 years or so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I hoped to be rich.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Because we hoped-- we were-- we were not very poor, but we were not rich.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my father knew how to daven.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He knew how to pray and shiva.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was never in-- she didn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She didn't know how to read.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in my house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "News-- that was luxury.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That cost money.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we used to get, like, you know, from my-- my sister, especially, from a friend or so.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She-- they had a newspaper, so she took-- you know, she borrowed it, so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And every news, you know what-- what happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't have radios in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we didn't have anything else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But was-- news, they always put them outside in the main streets, you know, like in the center of the city on poles like they still do it in Israel now--",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and announce so we knew what's going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some people-- I remember one family, I think, was-- was either rich, and they had the radios-- a radio.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody went to the house to listen to the news.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know what a telephone meant-- meant really-- a telephone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was Jewish, a Jewish paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a Jewish paper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Jewish paper.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not until [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] '40, 1940, I think when they came.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't, but my parents did because of everybody was interested to know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not-- not to my knowledge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe somebody else did, but I, myself, as a child I did not feel that there was any danger until the German came in.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
